      "content": "thanks. those are good general tips. but i'm trying to define what \"true\" sophistication looks like globally. if someone wants to be seen as a high-level professional anywhere in the world, what should be the baseline standard for things like dress, dining, and conversation? like, what is the quintessential \"sophisticated\" way to carry oneself?",
